"use client"

import { useState } from "react"
import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  FormControl,
  InputLabel,
  MenuItem,
  Select,
  TextField,
  Typography,
  CircularProgress,
} from "@mui/material"

const Plan = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate()
  const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
    businessName: "",
    industry: "",
    targetAudience: "",
    objectives: ["brand"],
    location: "Pune",
    campaignDuration: "1-week",
    budget: 10000,
    startDate: "",
    additionalInfo: "",
  })
  const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState(false)
  const [isComplete, setIsComplete] = useState(false)

  const handleChange = (e) => {
    setFormData({ ...formData, [e.target.name]: e.target.value })
  }

  const handleSubmit = async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault()
    setIsSubmitting(true)

    try {
      console.log("üöÄ Submitting form data:", formData)

      const response = await fetch("http://localhost:8080/api/chat/generateRoute", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: {
          "Content-Type": "application/json",
        },
        body: JSON.stringify(formData),
      })

      if (!response.ok) {
        const errorData = await response.json()
        console.error("‚ùå Error response data:", errorData)
        throw new Error(`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`)
      }

      const data = await response.json()
      console.log("‚úÖ API Response Data:", data) // Log the full response data

      // Log specific fields to verify data structure
      console.log("üìä Response Details:", {
        businessName: data.businessName,
        businessType: data.businessType,
        budget: data.budget,
        location: data.location,
        hasRoutePlan: Boolean(data.routePlan),
        routePlanLength: data.routePlan ? data.routePlan.length : 0,
      })

      setIsSubmitting(false)
      setIsComplete(true)

      // Store the response data in localStorage so CampaignResults can access it
      localStorage.setItem("campaignData", JSON.stringify(data))
      console.log("üíæ Data saved to localStorage")

      // Navigate to the results page after a short delay
      setTimeout(() => {
        console.log("üîÑ Navigating to campaign results page")
        navigate("/campaign-results")
      }, 1500)
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("‚ùå Error submitting form:", error)
      setIsSubmitting(false)
    }
  }

  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        maxWidth: 600,
        mx: "auto",
        mt: 4,
        p: 3,
        bgcolor: "background.paper",
        borderRadius: 1,
        boxShadow: 3,
      }}
    >
      <Typography variant="h4" align="center" gutterBottom>
        Create Your Marketing Plan
      </Typography>
      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
        <TextField
          fullWidth
          label="Business Name"
          name="businessName"
          value={formData.businessName}
          onChange={handleChange}
          margin="normal"
          required
        />
        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal" required>
          <InputLabel id="industry-select-label">Industry</InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="industry-select-label"
            id="industry"
            name="industry"
            value={formData.industry}
            label="Industry"
            onChange={handleChange}
          >
            <MenuItem value="restaurant">Restaurant/Cafe</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="retail">Retail</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="entertainment">Entertainment</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="education">Education</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="technology">Technology</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="healthcare">Healthcare</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="other">Other</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>
        <TextField
          fullWidth
          label="Target Audience"
          name="targetAudience"
          value={formData.targetAudience}
          onChange={handleChange}
          margin="normal"
          required
        />
        <TextField
          fullWidth
          label="Budget (‚Çπ)"
          name="budget"
          type="number"
          value={formData.budget}
          onChange={handleChange}
          margin="normal"
          required
        />
        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal" required>
          <InputLabel id="duration-select-label">Campaign Duration</InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="duration-select-label"
            id="campaignDuration"
            name="campaignDuration"
            value={formData.campaignDuration}
            label="Campaign Duration"
            onChange={handleChange}
          >
            <MenuItem value="1-day">1 Day</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="1-week">1 Week</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="2-weeks">2 Weeks</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="1-month">1 Month</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="3-months">3 Months</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal" required>
          <InputLabel id="objectives-select-label">Campaign Objective</InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="objectives-select-label"
            id="objectives"
            name="objectives"
            value={formData.objectives[0]}
            label="Campaign Objective"
            onChange={(e) => setFormData({ ...formData, objectives: [e.target.value] })}
          >
            <MenuItem value="brand">Brand Awareness</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="traffic">Store Traffic</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="launch">Product Launch</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="event">Event Promotion</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal" required>
          <InputLabel id="location-select-label">Location</InputLabel>
          <Select
            labelId="location-select-label"
            id="location"
            name="location"
            value={formData.location}
            label="Location"
            onChange={handleChange}
          >
            <MenuItem value="Pune">Pune</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Mumbai">Mumbai</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Delhi">Delhi</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Bangalore">Bangalore</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Chennai">Chennai</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="Hyderabad">Hyderabad</MenuItem>
          </Select>
        </FormControl>
        <TextField
          fullWidth
          label="Additional Information (Optional)"
          name="additionalInfo"
          value={formData.additionalInfo}
          onChange={handleChange}
          margin="normal"
          multiline
          rows={4}
        />
        <Button
          type="submit"
          variant="contained"
          color="primary"
          fullWidth
          disabled={isSubmitting}
          sx={{ mt: 3, py: 1.5 }}
        >
          {isSubmitting ? <CircularProgress size={24} color="inherit" /> : "Generate Plan"}
        </Button>
        {isComplete && (
          <Typography variant="subtitle1" align="center" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
            Plan generated successfully! Redirecting...
          </Typography>
        )}
      </form>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Plan
